## Overview of Search Atlas vs Surfer SEO

Search Atlas combines powerful content tools with end-to-end SEO capabilities. Surfer SEO excels at content scoring and AI-assisted writing within its editor but lacks native rank tracking, backlink analysis, site auditing, local SEO features, and automated execution. Search Atlas includes [Atlas Brain](/search-atlas/atlas-brain) for conversational strategy and execution, [Content Genius](/search-atlas/content-genius) for bulk AI content, [SEO topical maps](/search-atlas/seo-topical-maps), and [OTTO SEO AI](/search-atlas/otto-seo-ai) for automated fixes and publishing.

Search Atlas supports multiple user seats in every plan and offers higher limits on AI content generation at significantly lower per-article cost.

